{"tid":1633682,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"突急：城大人如果唔想比人再話垃圾就入嚟","createTime":"2019-10-07T04:52:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T07:12:33.000Z","uid":320299,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"068e41347995c0ab3c803440d5990e248aae62b8","tid":1633682,"uid":320299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:52:16.000Z","msg":"校長郭位之前話對話對到依加失哂蹤。<br />\n擺到明避開學生，但好奇怪學生又唔上門搵佢。<br />\n係 有一日話如果時限內唔回應就去鄭翼去校長室，但夠鐘喇啲人呢？我企撚左喺u-circle睇住啲傻閪喺到玩划艇機咋。唔講SU有幾廢，cbc等都唔會搞圍校長，唯有學生自發架咋。<br />\n<br />\n我唔知有幾多city學生比人拉，<br />\n我唔知呢個龜縮校方比到咩法律援助被捕人士，<br />\n<br />\n我已經唔求佢出嚟會有咩言論，佢鐘意譴責又好唔譴都好，呢個係城大人反抗嘅時候，樓下討論。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82ac686ac8028b1523b3abf421fff3c61afb0354","tid":1633682,"uid":320299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:53:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e2f005737073f62cbb5b8c18012b00e0ebdf71f3","tid":1633682,"uid":320299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:54:04.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"dedac3eb7856e471006282c9d63683c11d14e709","tid":1633682,"uid":320299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:54:15.000Z","msg":"時代革命"},{"pid":"c3c47fdc8dd98d2c83c00f3d001cab17e7758f0f","tid":1633682,"uid":320299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:55:12.000Z","msg":"秒沉 on9"},{"pid":"cb8dd02c2c666d57acb91f8206b267346bcd3e2e","tid":1633682,"uid":285267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:11:53.000Z","msg":"痴線完全冇人推 咁多間大學真係城大最垃圾 幾個月郭位仲可以留係office平行時空"},{"pid":"395d4c72e326fb3655704c793350d94e1fcd0438","tid":1633682,"uid":320299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb8dd02c2c666d57acb91f8206b267346bcd3e2e","tid":1633682,"uid":285267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:11:53.000Z","msg":"痴線完全冇人推 咁多間大學真係城大最垃圾 幾個月郭位